Package com.newrelic.api.agent

Class MessageConsumeParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.newrelic.api.agent.MessageConsumeParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExternalParameters
    public class MessageConsumeParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExternalParameters
    Creates the parameters to report a message that was pulled from a message queue. This should be used with TracedMethod.reportAsExternal(ExternalParameters). A fluent builder is provided to allow for easy usage and management of this API.
    Since:
    3.36.0
